onal design with two dimensional\n(2D) (horizontal) maneuver only, by exploiting the additional degrees of\nfreedom in altitudes. It is also shown that the non-colluding and colluding\neavesdroppers lead to distinct 3D UAV maneuver behaviors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Dec 2019 19:39:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-03"}
